:{{DIcon|Talk}} Has business been going well lately?
:::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 502064201: Config/Level/NPCDialogue/P10202/NPCAct/Act502064201.json-->
:::'''Tall Auntie:''' My business is booming! More and more tourists are flocking the Aurum Alley, and our authentic Luofu snacks are selling like hotcakes!
:::'''Tall Auntie:''' The storytelling and crosstalk comedy sessions you arranged for me are well-received too. Some people sit down and order something to eat just because they are drawn to the performances. That makes our business even better.
:::<!--Ends the current performance-->
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: Talk_502064201-->
:;(If {{Mission|Back in Business (IV)|showChapter=0}} has been completed)
:{{DIcon|Exit}} I don't have an appetite now.
:::'''Tall Auntie:''' Thank you for stopping by!
:::<!--Ends the current performance-->
